2020年12月25日圣诞节当日清晨，美国[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]第二大城市[[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]市区一栋[[AT&T|AT&T]]通讯大楼前发生一起'''[[自杀攻击|自杀式爆炸]]案件'''。炸弹被安装在一辆停在路边的[[旅居车|旅居车]]上，由于适逢圣诞节清晨，街上鲜有行人，除袭击者自己身亡外，爆炸仅造成3人受伤，沿街的数栋建筑物受损。<ref name="Andone"/><ref name="AP.Interest">{{cite news|url=https://apnews.com/article/us-news-nashville-coronavirus-pandemic-tennessee-dc6eb653053967a4187f0ca8276d20a8|title=FBI at home of possible person of interest in Nashville bomb|publisher=Associated Press|last1=Kruesi|first1=Kimberlee|last2=Balsamo|first2=Michael|last3=Tucker|first3=Eric|date=2020-12-26|access-date=2020-12-26|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212246/https://apnews.com/article/us-news-nashville-coronavirus-pandemic-tennessee-dc6eb653053967a4187f0ca8276d20a8|dead-url=no}}</ref>爆炸前有目击者听到枪声，且从发生爆炸的旅居车传出大声的警告语音，称炸弹即将爆炸，让附近的人员尽速离开。<ref name="Andone">{{Cite web|first1=Dakin|last1=Andone|first2=Hollie|last2=Silverman|first3=Steve|last3=Almasy|title=Possible human remains found near Nashville explosion site, police chief says|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/25/us/nashville-explosion/index.html|date=2020-12-25|access-date=2020-12-25|website=CNN|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212133/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/25/us/nashville-explosion/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-12-25|title=Nashville Tennessee RV Explosion 'Intentional Act' Say Police, Downtown Evacuated|url=https://www.newsweek.com/nashville-tennessee-explosion-building-collapse-fire-1557290|access-date=2020-12-25|first=Khaleda|last=Rahman|website=Newsweek|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212136/https://www.newsweek.com/nashville-tennessee-explosion-building-collapse-fire-1557290|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/nashville-police-investigating-christmas-morning-vehicle-explosion-n1252357|title=Nashville police investigating 'intentional' Christmas morning vehicle explosion|last=Einhorn|first=Erin|publisher=NBC News|date=2020-12-25|accessdate=2020-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212143/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/nashville-police-investigating-christmas-morning-vehicle-explosion-n1252357|dead-url=no}}</ref>爆炸案发生后，由[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]主持负责调查，三天后警方公布认为63岁的市民安东尼·奎因·华纳（{{lang|en|Anthony Quinn Warner}}）一人单独策划了这起爆炸，且已在爆炸中当场死亡。<ref name=NPRName>{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/12/27/950606960/authorities-name-suspect-in-nashville-blast-suspect-explosion-was-a-suicide-bomb|first=Matthew S.|last=Schwartz|title=Nashville Blast Suspect Died In Explosion, Officials Say|date=2020-12-27|work=NPR|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231014806/https://www.npr.org/2020/12/27/950606960/authorities-name-suspect-in-nashville-blast-suspect-explosion-was-a-suicide-bomb|dead-url=no}}</ref>
