==经过==
根据附近的监视记录，一辆旅居车凌晨1点22分停靠在[[AT&T|AT&T]]大楼门外。<ref name=nytdec25>{{Cite news|last=McGee|first=Jamie|last2=Rojas|first2=Rick|last3=Tompkins|first3=Lucy|last4=Taylor|first4=Derrick Bryson|date=2020-12-25|title=Nashville Explosion Appears Intentional, Authorities Say|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/25/us/nashville-explosion.html|access-date=2020-12-25|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225144120/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/25/us/nashville-explosion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>数小时后，车上传来[[语音合成|人工语音]]：“请尽快撤离，这里有炸弹。这辆车里有一枚炸弹即将引爆。”<ref name="Andone" /><ref name=nytdec25/><ref>{{cite news |last1=Tamburin |first1=Adam |title=Exclusive: Nashville explosion witness remembers chilling warning from the RV: 'A bomb is in this vehicle' |url=https://www.tennessean.com/story/news/crime/2020/12/25/nashville-explosion-witness-remembers-chilling-warning-evacuate-now/4045368001/ |access-date=2020-12-25 |work= |date=2020-12-25 |archive-date=2020-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212145/https://www.tennessean.com/story/news/crime/2020/12/25/nashville-explosion-witness-remembers-chilling-warning-evacuate-now/4045368001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title='This vehicle will explode in 15 minutes.' Witnesses describe surviving the Nashville explosion|url=https://www.wrcbtv.com/story/43101364/this-vehicle-will-explode-in-15-minutes-witnesses-describe-surviving-the-nashville-explosion|publisher=CNN|via=WRCB|date=2020-12-25|accessdate=2020-12-26|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212216/https://www.wrcbtv.com/story/43101364/this-vehicle-will-explode-in-15-minutes-witnesses-describe-surviving-the-nashville-explosion|dead-url=no}}</ref>5点30分，当地警察接到报警正在调查附近的枪声。在听到车上喇叭的警告后，警方疏散了附近一些居民楼的民众。<ref name="Andone" />

6点30分，拆弹小组还没有到达现场，旅居车上的炸弹就引爆了，<ref name="Hawkins1225220">{{Cite news|last1=Hawkins|first1=Derek|last2=Firozi|first2=Paulina|last3=Kranish|first3=Michael|date=2020-12-25|title=RV that exploded in Nashville broadcast a message warning of imminent blast, police say|newspaper=The Washington Post|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/12/25/nashville-explosion-christmas/|accessdate=2020-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225200902/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/12/25/nashville-explosion-christmas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>当时在车内的安东尼·奎因·华纳当场死亡，附近有3人受伤，包括一名警察被冲击波震倒在地。<ref name=nprdec25>{{cite news|last=Oxner|first=Reese|date=2020-12-25|title=Explosion In Downtown Nashville, Believed To Be 'Intentional,' Injures At Least 3|publisher=NPR|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/12/25/950286247/explosion-in-downtown-nashville-believed-to-be-intentional-injures-at-least-3|accessdate=2020-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212228/https://www.npr.org/2020/12/25/950286247/explosion-in-downtown-nashville-believed-to-be-intentional-injures-at-least-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>有人在社交媒体上上传监控视频显示，爆炸产生的碎片飞散到了两个街区外的楼顶。<ref name=tennesseandec25>{{Cite web|last=Medina|first=Daniella|date=2020-12-25|title=Nashville residents capture confusion, chaos in moments after downtown explosion|url=https://www.tennessean.com/story/news/local/2020/12/25/nashville-explosion-christmas-photo-video-footage/4044769001/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212247/https://www.tennessean.com/story/news/local/2020/12/25/nashville-explosion-christmas-photo-video-footage/4044769001/|archive-date=2020-12-27|access-date=2020-12-25|website=The Tennessean|language=en-US|dead-url=no}}</ref>另外爆炸造成至少三辆汽车起火，附近41家商户受损，以及附近的一栋房屋倒塌。<ref name="Andone" /><ref name=nytdec25/>

==调查==
爆炸发生后，赶到现场的拆弹分队，当地警方和联邦探员展开收集证据的工作。<ref name="tennesseandec25" /><ref name=CNN.Identified/><ref name="reutersdec25">{{cite news|last1=McKay|first1=Rich|last2=Johnson|first2=Katanga|title=Motor home explodes in Nashville, possible human remains found near site|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2020-12-25|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-tennessee-blast-idUSKBN28Z0SB|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201225153551/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-tennessee-blast-idUSKBN28Z0SB|dead-url=no}}</ref>在清理了现场之后没有发现更多的爆炸物。<ref name="warner.cnn">{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/27/us/nashville-explosion-what-we-know/index.html|title=Here's what we know about the Nashville explosion and investigation|publisher=CNN|last=Maxouris|first=Christina|date=2020-12-27|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212204/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/27/us/nashville-explosion-what-we-know/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>调查人员有发现空的弹壳，但随后被认定只是在爆炸中被破坏的子弹。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pegues|first1=Jeff|last2=Triay|first2=Andres|date=2020-12-26|title=Nashville bombing suspect may have been killed in blast, sources say|work=CBS News|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/nashville-bombing-person-of-interest-identified/|access-date=2020-12-26|archive-date=2020-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226174608/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/nashville-bombing-person-of-interest-identified/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在事发现场，调查人员提取到了人体组织，<ref name="AP.Interest" />随后根据[[DNA|DNA]]比对，证实这些组织属于炸弹客安东尼·奎因·华纳自己。用于安放炸弹的汽车上，警方取证的[[车辆识别号码|车辆识别号码]]也证实车辆属于安东尼本人。<ref name="death.tennessean"/><ref name=CNN.Identified>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/27/us/nashville-explosion-what-we-know/index.html|title=Anthony Quinn Warner identified as Nashville bomber|publisher=CNN|last1=Ellis|first1=Ralph|last2=Maxouris|first2=Christina|last3=Silverman|first3=Hollie|last4=Andone|first4=Dakin|date=2020-12-27|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227212204/https://www.cnn.com/2020/12/27/us/nashville-explosion-what-we-know/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

联邦调查局宣布将这起案件定性为[[自杀攻击|自杀攻击]]，<ref name="death.tennessean"/>现场周边调取的监控录像也显示，只有安东尼一人制造的这起爆炸案。<ref name=LoneBomber>{{Cite news|first=Natalie|last=Allison|url=https://www.tennessean.com/story/news/crime/2020/12/27/anthony-quinn-warner-confirmed-person-interest-nashville-explosion/4052711001/|title=Anthony Quinn Warner, self-employed computer guru ID's as lone Nashville bomber, killed in blast|newspaper=The Tennessean|date=2020-12-27|access-date=2020-12-27|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231014936/https://www.tennessean.com/story/news/crime/2020/12/27/anthony-quinn-warner-confirmed-person-interest-nashville-explosion/4052711001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

